  "query_complexity": "SIMPLE",
  "was_decomposed": true,
  "final_sql": "WITH latest_per_account AS (     SELECT         acnt_code,         customer_name,         principal,         rate,         status,         ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY acnt_code ORDER BY txn_date DESC) AS rn     FROM dbm.loan_balance_detail     WHERE status = 'O' AND principal IS NOT NULL ),  latest_principal AS (     SELECT         customer_name,         principal * rate AS principal_in_mnt     FROM latest_per_account     WHERE rn = 1 )  SELECT     customer_name,     SUM(principal_in_mnt) AS total_principal_in_mnt FROM latest_principal GROUP BY customer_name ORDER BY total_principal_in_mnt DESC FETCH FIRST 1 ROW ONLY;",
  "result_count": 1,
  "final_answer": "Таны хүсэлтийн дагуу хамгийн өндөр зээлийн үлдэгдэлтэй зээлдэгчийн мэдээллийг хүргэж байна:  - Зээлдэгчийн нэр: ДЦС-4 ТӨХК   - Зээлийн үлдэгдэл (төгрөгөөр): 253,309,397,578.54"
